@startuml
actor 用户 as User
participant "工作台 UI" as UI
participant "运行 API" as API
participant "工作流执行器" as Runner

User -> UI: 点击运行
UI -> API: POST /api/runs/workflow
API -> Runner: 启动执行
Runner --> API: 步骤事件 (start/end/failed/agent_output)
API --> UI: SSE 事件 (/api/runs/{id}/stream)
UI -> UI: 更新节点状态 + 日志面板
UI --> User: 运行结果 + 摘要
@enduml
